#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="38"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.7"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:45.1"
msgid "‘Yathā vā paneke bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā saddhādeyyāni bhojanāni bhuñjitvā te evarūpaṃ jūtappamādaṭṭhānānuyogaṃ anuyuttā viharanti, seyyathidaṃ—"
